title: Advisor Roster
new-page: true
is-card: true
is-pinned-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/placeholder.jpg
view-if: started and advisor_roster_timer <= 0

= Advisor Roster

The SLD can keep **[+ max_advisors +]** active advisors. Changing the roster uses this month's action and locks roster changes for six months.

Active advisors: [+ n_advisors +] / [+ max_advisors +]

Recruit or release advisors:

- @recruit_czarzasty: Recruit Wlodzimierz Czarzasty.
- @recruit_trela: Recruit Tomasz Trela.
- @recruit_jonski: Recruit Dariusz Jonski.
- @recruit_biedron: Recruit Robert Biedron.
- @recruit_wanda_nowicka: Recruit Wanda Nowicka.
- @recruit_barbara_nowacka: Recruit Barbara Nowacka.
- @recruit_ikonowicz: Recruit Piotr Ikonowicz.
- @recruit_kwasniewski: Recruit Aleksander Kwasniewski.
- @recruit_belka: Recruit Marek Belka.
- @recruit_cimoszewicz: Recruit Wlodzimierz Cimoszewicz.
- @release_miller: Release Leszek Miller.
- @release_gawkowski: Release Krzysztof Gawkowski.
- @release_senyszyn: Release Joanna Senyszyn.
- @release_czarzasty: Release Wlodzimierz Czarzasty.
- @release_trela: Release Tomasz Trela.
- @release_jonski: Release Dariusz Jonski.
- @release_biedron: Release Robert Biedron.
- @release_wanda_nowicka: Release Wanda Nowicka.
- @release_barbara_nowacka: Release Barbara Nowacka.
- @release_ikonowicz: Release Piotr Ikonowicz.
- @release_kwasniewski: Release Aleksander Kwasniewski.
- @release_belka: Release Marek Belka.
- @release_cimoszewicz: Release Wlodzimierz Cimoszewicz.
- @root: Return to main.

@recruit_czarzasty
title: Recruit Wlodzimierz Czarzasty
view-if: n_advisors < max_advisors and czarzasty_advisor = 0
on-arrival: {!
Q.czarzasty_advisor = 1;
Q.n_advisors += 1;
Q.advisor_roster_timer = 6;
Q.month_actions += 1;
Q.sld_apparatus_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_strength + 0.3);
Q.sld_apparatus_tension = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_tension - 6);
Q.sld_modernizers_tension = Math.min(150, Q.sld_modernizers_tension + 4);
!}

Czarzasty joins the active advisor roster as an apparatus and media operator.

- @post_event: Continue.

@recruit_trela
title: Recruit Tomasz Trela
view-if: n_advisors < max_advisors and trela_advisor = 0
on-arrival: {!
Q.trela_advisor = 1;
