Q.sld_modernizers_tension = Math.max(0, Q.sld_modernizers_tension - 5);
Q.sld_apparatus_tension = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_tension - 3);
!}

Trela joins the active advisor roster as a regional and mid-generation organizer.

- @post_event: Continue.

