@release_miller
title: Release Leszek Miller
view-if: miller_advisor = 1
on-arrival: {!
Q.miller_advisor = 0;
Q.n_advisors = Math.max(0, Q.n_advisors - 1);
Q.advisor_roster_timer = 6;
Q.month_actions += 1;
Q.sld_apparatus_tension = Math.min(150, Q.sld_apparatus_tension + 16);
Q.gawkowski_network_strength = Math.min(10, Q.gawkowski_network_strength + 0.3);
!}

Miller leaves the active advisor roster. The apparatus treats this as a direct political signal.

- @post_event: Continue.

